            <p><div class="content_para"><p>This is the current release of the guideline.</p>
<p>This guideline updates a previous version: Management of Overweight and Obesity Working Group. VA/DoD clinical practice guideline for screening and management of overweight and obesity. Washington (DC): Department of Veterans Affairs, Department of Defense; 2006. 117 p.</p>
<p>This guideline meets NGC's 2013 (revised) inclusion criteria.</p></div></p>
