, <a href="/web/20180712211208/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_MTH_CUI=C0016745&amp;fLockTerm=Fructose">Fructose</a>
, <a href="/web/20180712211208/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_MTH_CUI=C0023676&amp;fLockTerm=Life+Style">Life Style</a>
, <a href="/web/20180712211208/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_MTH_CUI=C0025102&amp;fLockTerm=Medical+Records">Medical Records</a>
